<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>1008</hymn_number>
<title>xī yáng xī xià shí 迦南1008</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 xī yáng xī xià shí, jiāng biān dú shēn yǐng.
 wèn liú shuǐ wèn qīng fēng hé qù yòu hé cóng.
 liú shuǐ gào sù wǒ, yào dào dà hǎi zhōng.
 qīng fēng yě lái gào sù wǒ, qù chuán dì zhǔ de ēn qíng.
 wǒ dī tóu jìng sī, shèng líng zài wǒ xīn zhōng gǎn dòng.
 zhǔ yé sū shì wǒ de dà mù zhě, shí jiān yǐ zhèng míng.
 gēn suí tā zhǐ guǎn xiàng qián xíng, bù kàn rén yě bù kàn huán jìng.
 zhǔ gěi de shǐ mìng, yī dìng yào wán chéng. yī dìng yào wán chéng.</lyrics>
</song>